Package: ledspicer
Architecture: any
Depends:
	${shlibs:Depends},
	${misc:Depends}
Description: LED Manager for linux
 LEDSpicer is a program that will handle several LED controller boards to
 create animations, effects and display profiles, to be used with arcade
 cabinets, or other projects that require an interaction with their
 LEDs controllers.
 .
 This package will install the following binaries:
  * ledspicerd (main daemon)
  * emitter (command line application to send commands to ledspicerd)
  * inputseeker (utility program to detect input devices and codes)

