Package: ledspicer-nanoled
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Priority: optional
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
 ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: Ultimarc NanoLed driver
 LEDSpicer is a program that will handle several LED controller boards to
 create animations, effects and display profiles, to be used with arcade
 cabinets, or other projects that require an interaction with their
 LEDs controllers.
 .
 This package will install the output plugin for the Ultimarc NanoLed, a
 60 leds controller.
 Install this package only if you own this hardware.

