Package: ledspicer-examples
Section: doc
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: Documentation and examples
 LEDSpicer is a program that will handle several LED controller boards to
 create animations, effects and display profiles, to be used with arcade
 cabinets, or other projects that require an interaction with their
 LEDs controllers.
 .
 This package contains documentation and some examples.
 I also include the sysmted service file and several data files to replace
 the default ones.

